Section: libs
Homepage: http://keckcaves.org/software/vrui

Package: SRCPKGNAME
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Vrui VR toolkit - Runtime
 The Vrui VR toolkit simplifies creation of portable and highly interactive
 fully-immersive virtual reality applications.
 .
 This package contains the runtime library files needed to run software
 using Vrui.

